ALL THE CONTRIBUTING UNCERTAINTIES IN QUADRATURE.THEY
ARE EXPRESSED WITH A 68% CONFIDENCE LEVEL,AND CONSIST
OF A VARIABLE COMPONENT,DUE TO COUNTING STATISTICS AND
PHOTOPEAK INTEGRATIONAS.
